name: That day in may when I learned about Wyckoff distribution
description: This is the first NFT created by 3X17 on the Tezos blockchain. This is the only edition of one NFT that will ever be created of this artwork on any blockchain. The website 3X17.com operates as the body authorised to authenticate the art of 3X17, handle contacts and states any extended use of the different images by 3X17 that is allowed in regards to copyright. The ID-number of this NFT in relation to 3X17 is no1. The royalties of this NFT after each sale is 10%. PNG-image, 2074x2074 pixels.
